bug.short_desc: Cell selection rectangle misaligned on browser zoom

long_desc.thetext: In Demo browser - table - Table increase vertical size of table. (pull down bottom border) than zoom in with (one or more Ctrl+) and select cell in one of the bottom rows. Cell selection rectangle has wrong dimension and wrong position. If we zoom back (with Ctrl 0) everything is OK.

Hi
Only Opera11 renders it correctly.
And here is description of problem and maybe solution to it: http://blogs.msdn.com/b/ie/archive/2012/02/17/sub-pixel-rendering-and-the-css-object-model.aspx
